Package: rjcdm
Type: Package
Title: Reversible Jump MCMC for Item-Level Model Selection of CDMs
Version: 1.0
Date: 2026-03-31
Author: David Arthur
Maintainer: David Arthur <dbarthur@uw.edu>
Description: Performs model selection of CDMs using reversible jump MCMC. This can be used to select between the G-DINA, ACDM, DINA, and DINO models while incorporating prior information about model parameters.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.1.0), stats, tmvtnorm, pgdraw, utils
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
URL: https://github.com/darthur2/rjcdm
BugReports: https://github.com/darthur2/rjcdm/issues
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
